Walter F. FOSTER, Individually and as Vice President of Foster and Kleiser Co., Appellant, v. C. E. STEVENS COMPANY et al., Appellees. No. 7617. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. April 11, 1935. Morrison, Hohfeld, Foerster, Shuman & Clark and Herbert W. Clark, all of San Francisco, Cal., for appellant. Glensor, Clewe, Schofield & Van Dine, of San Francisco, Cal., and Caldwell & Lycette, of Seattle, Wash., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
